"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"As accelerating modern life, most people's lives every day to be away from work, rarely have the chance to go to outdoor sports, it has also led to a lot of pressure on people's lives is more and more big, there is no way to vent, so what has more exciting outdoor sports can make our adrenaline surge, release the pressure? Take a look at these!\\n\\n1. Fly low\\n\\nJumping from the top of a tall building to enjoy the thrill of surpassing the city's peak is of great interest to those who enjoy low-flying sports. But because of the lack of height, this sport can easily cause death and injury.\\n\\n1. The bungee jumping\\n\\nBungee jumping was born in the Pacific islands, vanuatu, aimed at the local young adult ceremony test their guts, can determine whether is qualified to be the benchmark in the face of crisis, for now is keen on this kind of \\\"game of death\\\", they need a strong heart, good blood vessels, and good luck, although bungee jumping with a lot of danger, of course, but as long as a medical no problem. Take precautions and you can still try it!\\n\\n1. Freehand rock climbing\\n\\nRock climbing is the sport originated in Europe, climbers to physical strength, courage, body coordination, flexibility, high requirements, the choice of today has become a popular outdoor sports, but the sport with the risk, it is a high threshold, so you want to rock climbing with his hands, and must do a good job in training, do not easily to try the sport.\\n\\n1. Diving\\n\\nHas always been considered reliable scuba diving has entered the \\\"movement\\\" death list, what a surprise, however, the sport in the challenge to human in underwater goes too far at the same time, the risk is very big also, scuba diving don't swim to the deep place, better completes the protective measures, such ability can reduce the risks of the sport.\\n\\nmountaineering\\n\\nMountain must be a challenge to human nature more directly, the cultivation of the body energy, breathing method, gait adjustment is indispensable to impact strength of valuable experience, but, even if have the above quality, mountaineering enthusiasts must also be in the face of great danger, it is snow mountain climate conditions of uncertainty, although mountaineering is a sport, But this sport is relatively reliable, if you have enough physical ability, you might as well try it.\\n\\nAlpine skiing.\\n\\nIt suddenly began to rain. Gliding on the snowy slope, the feeling seemed to be in competition with the wind. Skiing is very exciting, but challenging is extremely high, has strict requirements on the player's physical qualities, and need certain skiing skills base, suitable for good health, the pursuit of stimulation of fever players, the same movement with a certain risk, if the skill to master is bad, may fall from mountain, so if you don't have enough technology, don't easily to try.\\n\\nOf course, we need to know that the above outdoor sports have a very high threshold, if there is no good technology and knowledge as far as possible do not participate in, you can choose some simple outdoor sports to release the pressure in their hearts, such as travel, these relatively reliable outdoor sports are more suitable for the public.\",\"timestamp\":1639102969,\"title\":\"Do you all know about these exciting outdoor sports?\"},\"digest\":\"PtKomFrJdlz2StCzgVJPJEMVCsqWuOKDiBE-yFAXAeg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x1f425fcF4695413316CcFB40b6E14572142a5aF3\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"P7_8zyE_HlaHFKKyGD16ik9nN3H6XaqEoOK4xvSUIsA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"UYeYICf9vO20HYNXF8OR54XMgxNUyqk645aQ9WyiSVQ\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"a7yATIEgFaOBykne5Fo_da8XHfWAwbitGA7YHSCZtocPgLtvzAB99YNFfcrOcre83PE0pjBOBXL702f_CU_Jyg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x3a87c553eb27d9d69a2ec42e470248403b4dc70d8eee2ea5326ba12398ab6ebd156c4195572cab4f59aecf7ba21bc04351661ed3264c8ee257cf5520230ea9